Non-Qualifying


You should probably just fuck off at this point because you cannot really use, copy, modify, or even 
look at this code. If you fall into the requirements for this license, and are using any of the
software covered by it, an exception will be made if you provide non-conditioned substantial financial
aid (and volunteer labor) of no less than 20% of the organizations and C-level executive salaries to any 
non-affiliated third parties involved with any of the following efforts...
 - Ensures that every homeless person and animal in the US will have a safe place to live and receive the medical care they need
 - Ensures that every US citizen, and those who's intention or desire is to become a citizen, has access to the same quality
 of food that you would feed your own family.
 - Closes down every animal kill shelter and opens enough no-kill shelters (with any necessary medical care, spay/neuter, etc)
 - anything else that I think has a net positive effect like these. 
 
 Using the software without also meeting these means that you will need to give me the sum that results in 10,000,000,000 USD after taxes, every 5 years, so that I can use it toward the aforementioned efforts.
